dcterms:description: A database containing images of pollen grains captured using multifocal optical microscopy, used for detecting pollen grains in air samples.
dcterms:title: Pollen Image Database

dcterms:description: A dataset used for training the classification framework, containing various pollen types.
dcterms:title: Training Dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset containing pollen images that are known to belong to the training dataset, used for testing authentication.
dcterms:title: Inlier Dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset containing pollen images that do not belong to the training dataset, used for testing authentication.
dcterms:title: Outlier Dataset

dcterms:description: Sub-datasets created from the training dataset, used for testing the robustness of the classification framework.
